script.name: plugin.guilds.wbrowser.columise
script.sourceplaintext:
$page.id = get global variable: name='pageid.guilds' $CONFIG = get global variable: name='guilds.config'
$data = table alloc
$ignore = table alloc $ignore[SPARE LASER 1] = [TRUE] $ignore[SPARE LASER 2] = [TRUE] $ignore[Repair Laser] = [TRUE]
$main.type = [SSTYPE_LASER] $current.data = table alloc $data['lasers'] = $current.data gosub sub.DoList
$main.type = [SSTYPE_MISSILE] $current.data = table alloc $data['missiles'] = $current.data gosub sub.DoList
return $data
sub.DoList: $sub = get number of subtypes of maintype $main.type while $sub dec $sub = $ware = get ware from maintype $main.type and subtype $sub
do if $ignore[$ware] continue
if $a.onlyKnown skip if has $ware been discovered continue end
gosub sub.Doitem end endsub
sub.Doitem: $tData = table alloc $current.data[$ware] = $tData $value = sprintf: fmt='%s', $ware, null, null, null, null $tData['name'] = $value $tData['spacer'] = ' ' if $main.type == [SSTYPE_LASER] gosub sub.DoLaser else if $main.type == [SSTYPE_MISSILE] gosub sub.DoMissile end endsub
sub.DoLaser: $value = sprintf: fmt='%s', $ware, null, null, null, null $tData['laser'] = $value $value = create custom menu string type icon: type=Lasertower $tData['icon'] = $value $value = get range of laser $ware $text = convert metre to string: $value $ret = create new array, arguments=$text, $value, null, null, null $tData['range'] = $ret $value = get average price of ware $ware $text = convert number $value to string $text = sprintf: fmt='%s %s', $text, [Text.Credits], null, null, null $ret = create new array, arguments=$text, $value, null, null, null $tData['price'] = $ret $value = get default launch time difference for missile type: $ware $text = 60000 / $value $text = convert number $text to string $text = sprintf: pageid=$page.id textid=3316, $text, null, null, null, null $ret = create new array, arguments=$text, $value, null, null, null $tData['reload'] = $ret $reload = get default launch time difference for missile type: $ware $value = get hull damage of laser $ware $text = convert number $value to string with suffix $ret = create new array, arguments=$text, $value, null, null, null $tData['hull.damage'] = $ret $value = fixed multiply and divide: $value * 1000 / $reload $text = convert number $value to string with suffix $ret = create new array, arguments=$text, $value, null, null, null $tData['hull.damage.sec'] = $ret $value = get OOS hull damage of laser $ware $text = convert number $value to string with suffix $ret = create new array, arguments=$text, $value, null, null, null $tData['hull.damage.oos'] = $ret $value = fixed multiply and divide: $value * 1000 / $reload $text = convert number $value to string with suffix $ret = create new array, arguments=$text, $value, null, null, null $tData['hull.damage.oos.sec'] = $ret $value = get shield damage of laser $ware $text = convert number $value to string with suffix $ret = create new array, arguments=$text, $value, null, null, null $tData['shield.damage'] = $ret $value = fixed multiply and divide: $value * 1000 / $reload $text = convert number $value to string with suffix $ret = create new array, arguments=$text, $value, null, null, null $tData['shield.damage.sec'] = $ret $value = get OOS shield damage of laser $ware $text = convert number $value to string with suffix $ret = create new array, arguments=$text, $value, null, null, null $tData['shield.damage.oos'] = $ret $value = fixed multiply and divide: $value * 1000 / $reload $text = convert number $value to string with suffix $ret = create new array, arguments=$text, $value, null, null, null $tData['shield.damage.oos.sec'] = $ret $value = get laser maximum energy: laser=$ware $text = convert number $value to string $text = sprintf: pageid=[Page.Menus] textid=962, $text, null, null, null, null $ret = create new array, arguments=$text, $value, null, null, null $tData['energy'] = $ret $value = get bullet energy consumption: bullet=$ware $value = fixed multiply and divide: $value * 1000 / $reload $text = convert number $value to string with suffix $text = sprintf: fmt='%s/%s', $text, [Text.Second], null, null, null $ret = create new array, arguments=$text, $value, null, null, null $tData['consumption'] = $ret
$value = get bullet speed of laser $ware $text = convert number $value to string $text = sprintf: fmt='%s %s', $text, [Text.MPS], null, null, null $ret = create new array, arguments=$text, $value, null, null, null $tData['speed'] = $ret $ammo = get ammunition of laser $ware if not $ammo $ret = create new array, arguments=[Text.No], 0, null, null, null $tData['has.ammo'] = $ret $ret = create new array, arguments='-', 0, null, null, null $tData['ammo'] = $ret else $ret = create new array, arguments=[Text.Yes], 1, null, null, null $tData['has.ammo'] = $ret $text = sprintf: fmt='%s', $ammo, null, null, null, null $ret = create new array, arguments=$ammo, $ammo, null, null, null $tData['ammo'] = $ret end
$value = get laser restrictions: laser=$ware if $value skip if size of table $value $value = null end
if not $value $text.cols = 'All' gosub sub.GetRaces $value = convert array to table: $aRaces, increment=[FALSE] else
$text.cols = array alloc: size=1 $text.cols[0] = '#COLUMN#'
$start.pos = 0
$table.races = table alloc
gosub sub.GetRaces $r = 0 $size = size of array $aRaces while $r < $size $race = $aRaces[$r] inc $r = $race.id = get race id for race: $race
if $value skip if $value[$race] continue end
$val = sprintf: fmt='sec_col.%s.captial', $race.id, null, null, null, null $colour = $CONFIG[$val] if $colour $table.races[$race] = [TRUE] $text = create custom menu string rect: width=6 y=0 height=12 menu colour=[MenuColour.Black] $text = create custom menu column string, position=$start.pos length=12 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text append $text to array $text.cols $text = create custom menu string rect: width=4 y=1 height=10 raw colour=$colour inc $start.pos = $text = create custom menu column string, position=$start.pos length=10 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text append $text to array $text.cols $start.pos = $start.pos + 9 end end $value = $table.races end
$ret = create new array, arguments=$text.cols, $value, null, null, null $tData['races'] = $ret endsub
sub.DoMissile: $value = sprintf: fmt='%s', $ware, null, null, null, null $tData['missile'] = $value $value = create custom menu string type icon: type=Fighter Drone $tData['icon'] = $value endsub
sub.GetRaces: $aRaces = get race array: include fixed=[FALSE], include corporations=[FALSE], include player=[FALSE] $sub.r = size of array $aRaces while $sub.r dec $sub.r = $sub.race = $aRaces[$sub.r] $sub.flags = get race flags: race=$sub.race if $sub.flags & [RaceFlg.Inactive] remove element from array $aRaces at index $sub.r end end endsub
return null
